# To-Do List

## Description
This is a simple To-Do List application developed using Python. It allows users to manage their daily tasks through a menu-driven program.

## Features
- Add a new task
- View all tasks
- Delete a task
- Exit the application

## Requirements
- Python 3.x
- Visual Studio Code (optional)

## How to Run
1. Open the project folder in VS Code.
2. Open the terminal.
3. Run the command:
   py main.py

